ed;\">機界賤種</span></span>喇"},{"pid":"f92aa6aa4c5822e192d18b0096d1d449775234c1","tid":195020,"uid":89861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T12:50:12.000Z","msg":"泰菜都吊打中菜"},{"pid":"d504bfff11d9724f0d6910d14c3e2d6193a560d0","tid":195020,"uid":5846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T12:55:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我最鐘意就係食日餐，其次就係西餐，之後就係廣東菜。中國菜？！who care囉唔該！！老老實實，廣東菜我都唔係咁鐘意食架咋</blockquote><br />\n連登仔真係on9無極限<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n廣東菜咪中菜嘅一種囉，瞓撚醒未呀？"},{"pid":"eb64c509a8e080be951053aa71a54100b1915fc3","tid":195020,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T14:16:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我最鐘意就係食日餐，其次就係西餐，之後就係廣東菜。中國菜？！who care囉唔該！！老老實實，廣東菜我都唔係咁鐘意食架咋</blockquote><br />\n連登仔真係on9無極限<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n廣東菜咪中菜嘅一種囉，瞓醒未呀？</blockquote><br />\n好明顯，我嘅意思就係，廣東菜唔係中菜"},{"pid":"387829a8d102d030598c998dec0222a6f3955cf9","tid":195020,"uid":5846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T02:44:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我最鐘意就係食日餐，其次就係西餐，之後就係廣東菜。中國菜？！who care囉唔該！！老老實實，廣東菜我都唔係咁鐘意食架咋</blockquote><br />\n連登仔真係on9無極限<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n廣東菜咪中菜嘅一種囉，瞓醒未呀？</blockquote><br />\n好明顯，我嘅意思就係，廣東菜唔係中菜</blockquote><br />\n香港人係其中一種地球人，咁香港人係咪地球人？"},{"pid":"b44d7a7687b178c88707bec02538e27c8821c8e0","tid":195020,"uid":42734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T02:46:32.000Z","msg":"哦"},{"pid":"0b32504193428b4bde6dda2727dc684475eb3fab","tid":195020,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T02:52:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我最鐘意就係食日餐，其次就係西餐，之後就係廣東菜。中國菜？！who care囉唔該！！老老實實，廣東菜我都唔係咁鐘意食架咋</blockquote><br />\n連登仔真係on9無極限<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n廣東菜咪中菜嘅一種囉，瞓醒未呀？</blockquote><br />\n好明顯，我嘅意思就係，廣東菜唔係中菜</blockquote><br />\n香港人係其中一種地球人，咁香港人係咪地球人？</blockquote><br />\n班友吹奏「中菜」呢個概念分明係大中華意識形態餘毒未清 <br />\n<br />\n之前我都鬧過幾次架啦 <br />\n<br />\n就算香港人其實都有好多唔同鄉下 <br />\n但我覺得都要識分返唔同菜派系 唔能夠將中菜一概而論 然後拎去比較話法意日都唔夠砌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">廣東菜=/=中國菜，唔唔好將高質廣東菜同蝗蟲菜相提並論</span></span>"},{"pid":"6bdd44c601a64fa89e717b044b038451f9fcafae","tid":195020,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T02:54:30.000Z","msg":"根本人種論上中國菜根本無可能做到世界前列，仲話要第一 <br />\n人地鬼佬日本佬做野認真程度根本無得比 ，中國人爆少陣炸都偷笑啦 <br />\n係，家常便飯的確唔錯多選擇，但做到藝術級別根本無可能 <br />\n宜家全世界都用日本／歐美牌子既科技有原因架，煮飯同一個邏輯"},{"pid":"246f01cb2b732c5c85362ae03003bdddddde7062","tid":195020,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T02:55:34.000Z","msg":"香港人講既中菜、中餐基本等於粵菜，而粵菜又基本等於香港式既粵菜 <br />\n<br />\n所以到頭來都只係理解左做香港自身Ｄ菜式，只係無意識下以為香港粵菜真係可以代表到中國（中原／朝廷）菜而已 <br />\n<br />\n中國人心目既中國菜 唔係香港人心目中既中國菜 <br />\n<br />\n中國人心目既中國菜 = 餃子, 糖醋魚, 水煮魚 <br />\n<br />\n香港人心目既中國菜 = 雲吞麵, 白切雞... <br />\n(廣東以外既人, 根本唔食鹼水麵同緊緊熟既雞) <br />\n<br />\n中國人心目既中文 = 普通話, 簡體字 <br />\n香港人心目既中文 = 廣東話, 繁體字 <br />\n<br />\n表面好似認同同一樣既.. 中文, 中國菜 <br />\n<br />\n真係以為雙方有共同點? <br />\n<br />\n其實雙方諗既都唔同.. 俾文字遊戲呃左"},{"pid":"19b30454d19201e900915e7734e2a1100d416c89","tid":195020,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T02:57:08.000Z","msg":"一見到中菜我就反胃　 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所以我成日都食便當為主 <br />\n食日本野個種感覺，不知幾高人一等啊 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n食中菜？簡直就無辱我香港人呢個身份啊 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c470ca5fac49746db1d245bb42c828e059033fc6","tid":195020,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T02:58:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我最鐘意就係食日餐，其次就係西餐，之後就係廣東菜。中國菜？！who care囉唔該！！老老實實，廣東菜我都唔係咁鐘意食架咋</blockquote><br />\n連登仔真係on9無極限<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n廣東菜咪中菜嘅一種囉，瞓醒未呀？</blockquote><br />\n好明顯，我嘅意思就係，廣東菜唔係中菜</blockquote><br />\n香港人係其中一種地球人，咁香港人係咪地球人？</blockquote><br />\n一句到尾：你去河北搵戶人家食飯蒸魚比我睇 <br />\n大半個所謂中國都唔係食你所講既&quot;中菜&quot;"},{"pid":"99cbaa3dc5e864e76337c58d8bec314c55c5d8e5","tid":195020,"uid":97742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T03:03:38.000Z","msg":"鍾意食點心洗唔洗比你屌下 on9 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04fa226e44c601779afa49f9416d68d9e3786204","tid":195020,"uid":97742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T03:05:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一見到中菜我就反胃　 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所以我成日都食便當為主 <br />\n食日本野個種感覺，不知幾高人一等啊 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n食中菜？簡直就無辱我香港人呢個身份啊 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n <br />\n以為食日本野就等於高人一等 <br />\n依家連登仲多on9仔<br />\nOn9仔照下鏡先好去屌隔離登啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"472a54217d851e9b110dd62cb98813e3c78da606","tid":195020,"uid":17551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T16:45:25.000Z","msg":"同意樓主，中菜真係垃圾黎"},{"pid":"c93cf77609f225b812efdcea90575a74abfa933e","tid":195020,"uid":7555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T16:47:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我最鐘意就係食日餐，其次就係西餐，之後就係廣東菜。中國菜？！who care囉唔該！！老老實實，廣東菜我都唔係咁鐘意食架咋</blockquote><br />\n連登仔真係on9無極限<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n廣東菜咪中菜嘅一種囉，瞓醒未呀？</blockquote><br />\n好明顯，我嘅意思就係，廣東菜唔係中菜</blockquote><br />\n香港人係其中一種地球人，咁香港人係咪地球人？</blockquote><br />\n諗起三叔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 全球回收不包括香港"},{"pid":"8368c3a57406d5460a8f7c61246847cadfca78b1","tid":195020,"uid":41846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T16:54:33.000Z","msg":"中菜無可能係藝術<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n搵足啲料先講啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個人覺得粵、滬、魯菜喺色香味俱全<br />\n其實個人喜好啫 <br />\n踩到自己地方啲嘢一文不值啦"},{"pid":"e39a2889e8c1f40587073675c0d0c7f0229301be","tid":195020,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T07:23:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8986102aaacef1014058e4da40df8d2310dbc44d","tid":195020,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T09:05:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc90454e2e1087c7b14f0072719578018d233235","tid":195020,"uid":55533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T09:09:18.000Z","msg":"廣東菜先最正囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbe7582336e638458e73e655e7de4488a25d3db4","tid":195020,"uid":38337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T09:34:32.000Z","msg":"話中菜一文不值嗰啲，<br />\n有冇試過真係食 唔同省份嘅菜式先？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}